Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Andriy Grytsenko <andrej@rep.kiev.ua>
Build-Depends:
 debhelper (>= 8.9.0~), pkg-config, tcl-dev,
 liblua5.1-dev | liblua5.2-dev, gettext,
 libidn11-dev, zlib1g-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.6
Homepage: http://foxeye.sf.net
Vcs-Git: git://git.code.sf.net/p/foxeye/code
