Package: foxeye
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Universal modular network agent - binary package
 FoxEye now is multipurpose modular client or service for client-server type
 networks: IRC, ICQ, etc.  All you need to make IRC bot or ICQ client is few
 modules that implement functionality you want.
 .
 This package contains main daemon and few modules.

Package: foxeye-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, foxeye (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Universal modular network agent - development package
 FoxEye now is multipurpose modular client or service for client-server type
 networks: IRC, ICQ, etc.  All you need to make IRC bot or ICQ client is few
 modules that implement functionality you want.
 .
 This package contains development headers required to create modules.

